text: Chapayevo () is a rural locality (a selo) in Kidryachevsky Selsoviet, Davlekanovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 444 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == It is located 47 km from Davlekanovo, 3 km from Kidryachevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Davlekanovsky District
title: Chapayevo, Davlekanovsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
